These are Puzzles for 1x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-1-1::.
There 2 different types of food: pepper, onion
1. the person eating pepper is on the left of the person eating onion##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |    2    |
| Food   | pepper | onion |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-1-2::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: musical, adventure
1. the person watching adventure movies is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |   2    |
| Movie-Genre   | musical | adventure |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-1-3::.
